type: software
title: AI Monitor Pro
abstract: "A free, open-source, 100% local observability dashboard for AI coding agents. Tracks token usage, LLM costs, tool calls, session traces, and reasoning steps across Claude Code, Gemini CLI, OpenAI Codex, Cursor, GitHub Copilot, and more. No signup, no cloud, no telemetry."
